# Klipy GIF API key — SERVER-SIDE ONLY. Do NOT prefix with VITE_ (that would
# bundle it into client code). Get a key at https://partner.klipy.com .
# Consumed by the /api/klipy proxy: the Cloudflare Pages Function in prod and
# the Vite dev middleware locally (reads from .env.local).
KLIPY_API_KEY=
